{"title":"[NOIP 2018模拟赛] 小P上考场","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/462#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=462","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/462/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/462/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/462"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"小P一觉醒来发现已经到2018年11月10日了。今天是NOIP的比赛日，小P需要尽快赶往考场。\r\n小P家在a号路口，他会告诉你哪些路口是相联通的，距离是多少。NOIP的考场在b号路口，该市道路没有单行道。\r\n小P想让你帮他规划到考场的路线，他希望找到这条最短的路线以用最短时间抵达考场。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行四个整数n，m，a，b\r\n接下来每行三个数，x，y，c代表x路口到y路口之间有一条路距离为c"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一个数，小P家到考场的距离。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"**intput**\r\n\r\n```\r\n7 11 5 4\r\n\r\n2 4 2\r\n\r\n1 4 3\r\n\r\n7 2 2\r\n\r\n3 4 3\r\n\r\n5 7 5\r\n\r\n7 3 3\r\n\r\n6 1 1\r\n\r\n6 3 4\r\n\r\n2 4 3\r\n\r\n5 6 3\r\n\r\n7 2 1\r\n```\r\n\r\n**output**\r\n\r\n```\r\n7\r\n```\r\n\r\n"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"1<=n<=2500\r\n\r\n1<=m<=6200\r\n\r\n1<=a,b<=n"}]}